metadata.description: The Pug Apes are a rare cross between Canine and Ape, the perfect combination for genetic stability. They are special hyper-intelligent creatures with the unique abilities to master normal world operations and finally free themselves from human servitude. Leading their great escape from the human beings, 2500 Pug Apes intend to publicly break free and be the masters of their destiny
metadata.name: VaughnSimmons #159
